node.accessibility_caption: Photo by LA Bucket List 🌴 in Los Angeles, California with @bucketlisters, and @losangelesbucketlist. May be an image of text that says 'BUCKE+ LISTERS Step Into The Works Of Van Gogh At This Larger Than Life Exhibit'.

node.text:
Who wants to explore an immersive world of Van Gogh’s famous works?! ✨🎨🌌 Tickets to 'Immersive Van Gogh’ are now available at Bucketlisters.com or our link-in-bio.
Featuring over 500,000 cubic feet of projections illuminating the artist’s sunny landscapes, night scenes, portraits & more. #LABucketlist

node.text: Is Goat Yoga on your bucket list? 🐐🧘‍♀️You can now book an hour goat yoga class at BucketListers.com or our link-in-bio (First class is July 25th)! See more at our link-in-bio @LosAngelesBucketList #LA #GoatYoga
